@startuml
title Enrich Stage - State Machine Diagram (Current)
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #f7e9dc
  BorderColor #d9c2a8
}

[*] --> Input
Input --> Skipped : row is None
Input --> ExecuteOps : valid row

ExecuteOps --> NeedsResolve : ambiguous candidates
ExecuteOps --> Failed : strictness => FAILED
ExecuteOps --> Enriched : operations completed

NeedsResolve --> StoreSecrets
Enriched --> StoreSecrets
Failed --> Output
Skipped --> Output

StoreSecrets --> Output : stored or skipped with diagnostics
Output --> [*]

note right of NeedsResolve
Resolve is NOT done here.
Enrich emits hints in meta for ResolveStage.
end note

@enduml
